casebody.data:
No. 738,

Misc.

Coulter v. Nelson, Warden, et al. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General of California, and Robert R. Granucci and Horace Wheatley, Deputy Attorneys General, for respondents.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Fortas is of the opinion that in treating the papers as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari should be granted.
